Monitor Product Consumption in Near Real-Time with Digital Wallet

Now you can use Digital Wallet to monitor your product usage and detect trends over time for your consumption-based Salesforce products. Accessible through the Your Account app and Consumption Cards feature in the app launcher, Digital Wallet gives overviews and detailed breakdowns of your company’s product usage in near real-time.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions. Digital Wallet is available for Data Cloud consumption-based products. To learn more, see Digital Wallet-Enabled Products and Rate Cards.

Who: Digital Wallet is available to users with the View Consumption user permission. Your Account is available to users with the Manage Billing permission or the Your Account App Admin User permission set.

How: Use the App Launcher to find Consumption Cards (1). Alternatively, in the Your Account app, click the Consumption Cards tab or View Consumption Cards (2) from the tile on the Home page.
